casebody.data:
No. 902,

Mise.

Johnson v. Avery, Commissioner of Correction, et al. Karl P. Warden for petitioner. George F. McCanless, Attorney General of Tennessee, Thomas E. Fox, Deputy Attorney General, and David W. McMackin, Assistant Attorney General, for respondents.

C. A. 6th Cir. Motion for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Certiorari granted and case transferred to appellate docket.
